                <TextBlock Margin="5">choose between image recognition (less reliable, faster), game restart (safe, slow) and game restart .desktop (safe, slow, launches game with audio latency fixes) to reload lazer skin</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Margin="5">- choose .desktop file instead of automatic lazer executable path detection</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Margin="5">set lazer path</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Margin="5">general:</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Margin="5">hotkeys</TextBlock>
            </StackPanel>
        </TabItem>
    </TabControl>
</Window>
